H0.text: In past times a rabbit was what we’d call a baby bunny. What were adult bunnies called. Warren

H1.text: In past times a rabbit was what we’d call a baby bunny. What were adult bunnies called. Buck

H2.text: In past times a rabbit was what we’d call a baby bunny. What were adult bunnies called. Doe

H3.text: In past times a rabbit was what we’d call a baby bunny. What were adult bunnies called. Cony

A4.text: The term coney is a term for an adult rabbit used until the 18th century; rabbit once referred only to the young animals.
